{
  "texts": [
    "From this, we can infer a very similar performance of both evaluated models in the 5FCV strategy.",
    "In fact, the average values across the five traits and all predictors (E+G, E+G+GE) for the average metrics presented in Table 2 are very similar, approximately 0.0587 for NRMSE and 0.81 for Cor.",
    "In the LOEO strategy, the information of a complete environment was predicted with the rest of the environments in each trait.",
    "This was done with the GBLUP Equation 1 and DL Equation 2 under two predictors, the first with only line effect (G) and the second with environment plus line effect (E+G).",
    "The results are presented in Table 3 and Figures 4, 5."
  ]
